@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Welcome page";
}



<body>
    <header>
      <div class="page-content">
        <h1>Why Adopt a Pet?</h1>
        <h2>The Benefits of Adoption</h2>
        <p>Adopting a pet means saving a life and giving a loving animal a second chance. It's a fulfilling experience that brings joy to both the pet and the owner...</p>
        <h3>How to Adopt</h3>
        <p>Visit your local shelter, or explore adoption websites to find your new best friend...</p>
        <p>or click here</p>
        <a href="/Rescue" class="btn btn-primary">Find Pets</a>
      </div>
    </header>




<main>

  <div class="container marketing">


    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette pb-5 pt-5 ">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">Pets Bring Unconditional Love <span class="text-body-secondary"></span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Pets are more than just animals – they are family. They provide companionship, emotional support, and even improve our mental well-being. Whether it’s a playful dog or a calm cat, pets offer a bond that brings joy to every home. Adopting a pet is one of the most rewarding decisions you can make, offering them a second chance at happiness while enhancing your own life.

</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="~/images/cat1.jpg" class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto rounded" width="500" height="500" data-aos="zoom-in">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette pb-5 pt-5">
      <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">Adopting is a Lifesaver<span class="text-body-secondary"></span></h2>
        <p class="lead bg-white bg-opacity-50">Adopting a pet is not only a compassionate choice but also a life-changing one. Millions of pets in shelters are waiting for loving homes. By adopting, you’re giving a pet a chance to thrive in a safe environment. Every adoption helps reduce the number of homeless pets and saves lives. When you adopt, you change both the pet's life and your own forever.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1 pt-5">
        <img src="~/images/dog1.jpg" class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto  rounded" width="500" height="500" data-aos="zoom-in">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette pb-5 pt-5">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">The Power of Adoption: Stats that Matter <span class="text-body-secondary"></span></h2>
        <p >-Over 3 million pets are adopted each year in the U.S. alone.</p>
        <p >-70% of pets in shelters are cats and dogs, waiting for families to give them a home.</p>
        <p >-Adopting pets reduces the number of stray animals on the streets and improves the community.</p>
        <p class="lead">By adopting, you’re joining a global movement to create a better future for pets and their owners.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="~/images/dogsrunning.jpg" class="bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto rounded" width="500" height="500" data-aos="zoom-in">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    

  </div>


  

</main>


</body>







